title: Dugan's Travels Names 2015 Five Star Agents
text: Dugan's Travels Names 2015 Five Star Agents Dugan's Travels recently named 22 agents as Five Star Agents for 2015. Five Star Agents are selected based on their service to clients, sales, and commissions during a 12 month period. "Dugan's Travels success as a host travel agency is dependent on the success of each and every Dugan's agent," Jennifer Dugan owner of Dugan's Travels. RIO RANCHO, NM, September 29,   Dugan's Travels recently named 22 agents as Five Star Agents for 2015. Five Star Agents are selected based on their service to clients, sales, and commissions during a 12 month period. Jennifer Dugan, owner of Dugan's Travels, the managers, and the staff at Dugan's Travels applaud these agents for their exemplary achievements. Five Star Premier Agents Managers Circle Tina Becker * Carol Walsh * * Attended one or more exclusive Dugan's University seminars. "Dugan's Travels success as a host travel agency is dependent on the success of each and every Dugan's agent," says owner Jennifer Dugan. "The managers and the staff want to recognize Dugan's top agents and acknowledge their hard work, dedication, and determination to grow their businesses. Dugan's is on track for another great year and looks forward to seeing the Five Star Agents Program grow as more agents achieve their dreams of owning a successful travel business." Five Star Agents will be announced annually to recognize Dugan's top agents. In addition to a gift card, Five Star Agents receive the use of the Five Star agent logo, a recognition event and Dugan's University registration discount or waiver depending on the recognition level.Dugan's Travels is a hosting agency for independent travel agents and is a member of IATAN, CLIA, ARC, OSSN, NACTA, and Vacation.com. Jennifer Dugan, a travel agent since 1994, started Dugan's Travels to be a work-at-home mom yet still remain a part of the travel industry. Dugan's offers agents the ability to build a business while working at home, low startup costs, and a generous commission split. For more information please visit www.travelathome.com . # # #
